# LLM 을 이용한 은행 상담 맞춤, Persona 프로젝트

# Persona Banking Chatbot

A banking chatbot built with Claude API, Flask, and Prompt Engineering.

## Features

- Persona-based AI
- Knowledge-based responses (knowledge.txt)
- Claude Streaming API
- Flask
- Conversation History

## Tech Stack

- Python
- Flask
- Claude API
- Prompt Engineering
- SSE
